Information about the files that you find into this folder:

** dbfolder
This file contains the folder in which your database will be created
and loaded.
If you are running tests or debugging you would want to choose a 
temporary folder.

** port
This file contains the port number in which your database daemon will
work.

** start_database.sh
Script to start the database daemon, to create your database and to
load all the tables and data, functions, triggers and indexes.

** delete_database.sh
Script to drop all the tables, delete the database and stop the daemon.
